Linda wertheimer finishes trip across middle america .
Today linda wertheimer completes her week of traveling west along route fifty through the center of the nation .
She's been stopping along the way to talk to americans about their lives and about what they think of government and president clinton's first three months in office .
She's found most people want to give the president a chance but they concerned about the economy and how it affects them .
She also met some children in colorado who don't have politics on their mind at all .
